Roles and Responsibilities
Peter Sondergaard is Senior Vice President, Gartner Research. His focus is on developing market-leading advice; developing a global organization of more than 1,000 experts across IT, supply chain and marketing; and expanding the client base to more than 14,500 organizations across more than 80 countries. These initiatives have resulted in all-time-high levels of revenue for Gartner Research of more than $1.7 billion in 2015.
 

